Context: Ageand sex-matched C57BL/6 IL-10 / and wild type mice were transferred from a germ-free environment to a specific pathogen free condition.

Animal and experimental design Ageand sex-matched C57BL/6 IL-10 / and wild type mice were obtained from the Jackson Laboratory (Bar Harbor, Maine) and maintained in a GF animal facility at the Model Animal Research Center of Nanjing University (Nanjing, China).
